Use the standard library
This is how to string_sequence of n:
   Remember that result is ""
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that limit is sum of n and 1
   Do this limit times:
      When i is more than 0, then:
         Add result to 32
      End when
      Add result to tostring of i
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
